Quickstrike:





Quickstrike kept up a good pace, but still watched his surroundings warily. 
He felt good being able to go out and explore. He didn't like loosing his 
temper at base, and the only ones there to yell at were the females.

He saw a rather large rock formation in the distance. He slowed his pace and 
stopped to study it. "Say look at that." he said. He blinked at it. He 
zoomed in on it with his optics and found out that it was a cave. It had a 
pointed top and a rather open area around the front.

He nodded his head to Stingtra. "Wanna go check that out? Could be somethin' 
interestin'."
